translations: 空中黑客（BBC 纪录片《昆虫帝国》第四集）

sentences.sentence: During these three centuries, Norse voyagers from Northern Europe explored northern seas, settled Greenland, and visited North America.
sentences.translation: 在这三个世纪中，来自北欧的挪威航海者们探索了北部海域，在格陵兰岛定居，并到访北美。

sentences.sentence: And the "Bus Station" will be ready to receive Cosmic Voyagers!
sentences.translation: 并且这个【巴士站】将完全准备好接受宇宙的航行者！

sentences.sentence: They are different sorts of voyagers and respond to different influences.
sentences.translation: 他们是不同的旅行者，对不同的影响作出反应。
